lowtreshold = 0.11
hightreshold = 0.15
nys_acs$Poverty_Level<-ifelse(nys_acs$county_per_poverty<lowtreshold,"Low","Medium")
nys_acs$Poverty_Level<- ifelse(nys_acs$county_per_poverty>hightreshold && nys_acs$Poverty_Level == "Medium","High","Medium")

grouped_schools<- nys_schools %>%
  group_by(year)%>%
  mutate(z_math = scale(mean_math_score),z_ela = scale(mean_ela_score))%>%
  ungroup()

Merge datasets

merge_schools <- merge(grouped_schools, nys_acs, by = "county_name")
